editorialNotes.standard: We love learning about the celestial bodies in our own galaxy, but we’ve always dreamed of building our own. SPACE gives us the power to create stunningly detailed stars and planets, forging a virtual universe that follows the laws of astrophysics. It’s a heady thrill to be the master of our own miniature heavens—whipping up red dwarfs, gas giants, and comets that blaze through the cosmos at the tap of a finger.
